<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4585244>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Maximum likelihood tree of Dactylogyrus and Pseudodactylogyrus collected from East Asia based on partial 28S rDNA sequences, showing placement of newly obtained sequences from Dactylogyrus skrjabini Achmerow, 1954 (LC414156). Bootstrap values shown along the branches are based on 1000 replicates for the ML and NJ analysis. The corresponding GenBank accession numbers are shown next to each species" ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4585244/files/figure.png" .

